head_commit.message:
[build] set \`config.toml\` at AX_ROOT instead of current directory

We will invoke Cargo under AX_ROOT instead of cwd to complie these testcases actually.
So when the \`arceos-apps\` project in a subdirectory of AX_ROOT, the \`config.toml\` under the root of this project will not work.
